        "text": "The pilots admitted they had\ngoose pimples riding pick-a-back\non goose pimples. What's more,\nthey said one of their 20 passen-\ngers—C. L. McKelvie, of Colum-\nbus, Ohio—was awake and saw\nthe same thing."
      },
